Paper: hep-th/9206029

Date: 1992-06-05

Title: Differential Geometry on Linear Quantum Groups

Comments: 15 pages

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 25 (1992) 139-148

An exterior derivative, inner derivation, and Lie derivative are introducedon the quantum group $GL_{q}(N)$. $SL_{q}(N)$ is then found by constructingmatrices with determinant unity, and the induced calculus is found.